          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainty on the median energy in the",
                "foils increases along the stack and includes the",
                "cumulative effects the uncertainty of incident beam",
                "energy (+-0.2 MeV), uncertainty on stopping in each",
                "foil due to thickness variation (5%) and straggling",
                "effects.",
                "The overall estimation is an uncertainty of +-0.2 MeV",
                "for the first foils, increasing to +-2.5 MeV in the",
                "last foil."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty of the cross-sections were",
                "estimated taking the independent relative errors of the",
                "linearly contributing components."
              ]
            }
